    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-cared for by its previous owner. The exterior is clean with only minor stone chips on the hood and a few light surface scratches consistent with careful use. Inside, the cabin is in great shape, though there is some light wear on the driver's seat bolster. Mechanically, the car is sound, with a complete service history and tires that still have plenty of tread remaining. It drives smoothly and represents a dependable, high-quality option for anyone looking for a well-maintained vehicle without the new-car price tag.",
      "price": 34000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
